The '''All-Clown Squadron of Fun''' was the designation [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]], in the guise of "[[Bescat Offdurmin]]," gave to the ''ad hoc'' [[Squadron/Legends|squadron]] accompanying him from [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]] to the ''[[Errant Venture/Legends|Errant Venture]]'' in the [[Kuat system/Legends|Kuat system]]. The other ships in the "squadron" consisted of the [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-Wings]] of [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] and [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]] and the ''[[Pulsar Skate]]''.

